data.description: Charming Townhouse with an open floor plan that offers two bedrooms and 1.5 baths. The downstairs offers lots of space, laminate floors throughout, with a half bath and access door to the backyard that is fully fenced with shed and walking path that leads to a pond. Wood burning fireplace for cozy winter evenings. Windows, Roof, and HVAC all replaced in 2015. Hot water heater replaced in 2019. Property Association offers pool and playgrounds. Centrally located in Virginia Beach. Near military bases, shopping, interstate and schools.
